&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a fast-paced Sales Development Representative (SDR) with an entrepreneurial mindset to find new customers and opportunities. You’ll be searching for business while being an engaged member of the AI/ML community. You will prospect, qualify, and generate opportunities to support the overall growth of the business. While we are a fully remote company, we’re a collaborative team that thrives on in-person connection!&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1065&quot; data-end=&quot;1122&quot;&gt;You’ll need to be based in the San Francisco Bay Area&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to join us in the office on an as-needed basis and for team events.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
